title: Pit Bull RC 1.9" Raceline Combat Aluminum Wheels - Silver (4)
description: Ready for Combat? Waging war off road just became better than ever! Pit Bull RC’s 1.9 Combat beadlock wheels are ready to tackle any terrain you throw their way! Heading into battle with anything less my leave you dead on the side of the trail. Pit Bull RC has officially jumped feet first into the scale aluminum beadlock wheel world with our latest release! Pit Bull RC is proud to partner up with Raceline Wheels to bring you not one, but three, new licensed scale aluminum 1.9 beadlock wheels! Introducing the Clutch, Combat, and Ryno beadlock wheels! These are true scale replicas of Raceline’s awesome 1:1 wheels! Available in all black, with scale beadlock bolts, integrated faux machined locking hubs, and unbeatable scale looks! Includes everything required to build four complete wheels! Are you ready to take your scale R/C game to the next level?
